Class SampleDimensionType

java.lang.Object
org.opengis.util.CodeList<SampleDimensionType>
org.geotoolkit.coverage.SampleDimensionType
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<SampleDimensionType>
@Deprecated public final class SampleDimensionType extends org.opengis.util.CodeList<SampleDimensionType>
Deprecated.
This is a legacy type from OGC Grid Coverages Implementation specification 1.0.
Specifies the various dimension types for coverage values. For grid coverages, these correspond to band types.
Author:
Martin Desruisseaux (IRD)
